<HEADLINE> Jordan's Stock Market Closes Slightly Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, July 21 (Xinhua) -- Price index in market value on the
Amman Financial Market (AFM) closed at 180.65 points Tuesday, 0.36
point lower than that on Monday, the AFM daily report said.
</P>
<P>
