<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, July 21 (Xinhua) -- Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index on Tuesday went down by losing 100.43 points,
or 2.25 percent, to close at 4,377.96 points from that on Monday.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was over 74 trillion Turkish Liras (277 million
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index closed at 5,436.85, down 71.94 points,
or 1.3 percent, the industrial index closed at 3,660.54, down
95.99 points, or 2.47 percent, and the service index closed at
5,078.38, down 321.5 points, or 5.98 percent, from Monday's
closing. 
</P>
