Eckhard confirmed the finding, saying that the observers' bodies
have traces of fire wounds.
</P>
<P>
The four men were reportedly going from Garm to Tavildara
district to supervise compliance with the military protocol of a
peace agreement on the registration of opposition fighters and
their integration into the national armed forces. 
