Wuhan: min. 26 degrees C., max. 29 degrees C., torrential to
heavy rain, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hangzhou: min. 27 degrees C., max. 32 degrees C., thunder
shower, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Taipei: min. 26 degrees C., max. 36 degrees C., cloudy to
thunder shower, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 27 degrees C., max. 34 degrees C., cloudy to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 28 degrees C., max. 32 degrees C., cloudy to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.  
