<HEADLINE> Argentina to Apply Anti-Dumping to European Wheat Gluten </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, July 21 (Xinhua) -- The Argentine government has
decided to apply anti-dumping rights to European wheat gluten, as
it has found that the product's subsidized price has already
affected its wheat production.
</P>
<P>
