Rosa said the case was the first heroin confiscation in
Amazonas and the drugs would be taken by the drug dealers to
Rotterdam, the Netherlands.
</P>
<P>
He added that heroin elaborated in Colombia with Brazilian
poppy was sent to Europe and the United States via Brazil.
