Annan on Tuesday condemned in the strongest terms the act of
cold-blood murder of four U.N. personnel in Tajikistan.
</P>
<P>
According to sources from U.N. mission in Tajikistan, it has
now been confirmed that four members of the United Nations Mission
of Observers in Tajikistan (UNMOT) were murdered. preliminary
investigations by UNMOT indicate that the patrol members were
